'''Yubicon''' was [[Roy Teda]]'s chief of staff on the planet [[Romin]].

[[General/Legends|General]] Yubicon led the defense against the [[Citizens' Resistance]], which, during the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[mission to Romin]] in [[24 BBY/Legends|24 BBY]], launched an assault on "Great Leader" Teda's corrupt, oppressive regime. Yubicon escaped the conflict, however, with Teda and the galactic criminal and mad [[Scientist/Legends|scientist]] [[Jenna Zan Arbor]].

Later, when the Jedi cover of impersonating the [[Slams|Slam gang]] was blown, and Zan Arbor had confiscated their [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsabers]] and they were being escorted into a Romin [[Prison/Legends|prison]], Yubicon was knocked out cold by Jedi [[Siri Tachi/Legends|Siri Tachi]] when the Jedi struck back to recover their lightsabers and break out of a prison they'd scarcely spent time in.

